Long Post!!

When I first started Open Relationship Podcast I knew that it would become something great. I just didn’t know it would have happened so fast. I wanted to build a community where EVERYONE has a voice whether it was right, wrong, or indifferent. When I read the comments from all of the LGBTQ+ community it truly makes my heart fills with joy. I’m not ever here to tell someone to agree with any of what we have to say. The fact that you are talking about the topic brings me joy. It takes a lot to be in front of a camera or microphone to voice your true opinions. I’m forever humble and grateful to our wonderful community which is our OPENERS! Openers keep doing what you are doing. We TRULY APPRECIATE AND LOVE YOU ALL! 
.
.
.
